      "text": "### **Implementation Quality (Post-Phase 24):**\n\n- ✅ Secure credential handling via `SecureCredentialStore`\n- ✅ Rate limiting integrated (`RateLimitedProvider` wrapper)\n- ✅ Circuit breaker pattern (`CircuitBreakerProvider`)\n- ✅ Configurable timeouts per provider\n- ✅ Input validation (`InputValidator` schemas)\n- ✅ Structured logging and observability\n\n### 2. Configuration System\n\n### **Current Capabilities:**\n\n```toml\n# exa.config.toml\n[system]\nversion = \"1.0.0\"\nlog_level = \"info\"\n\n[agents]\ndefault_model = \"default\"  # References [models.default]\ntimeout_sec = 60\n\n[models.default]\nprovider = \"mock\"\nmodel = \"mock-model\"\n\n[models.fast]\nprovider = \"mock\"\nmodel = \"mock-fast\"\n\n[models.local]\nprovider = \"ollama\"\nmodel = \"llama2\"\n\n[database]\nbatch_flush_ms = 100\nbatch_max_size = 100",
